author: Fextralife
description:
10 RPGS Where CHOICES Actually MATTER
In this Fextralife video, we're going to be taking a look at RPGs where your choices actually matter. There are RPGS where choices feel like a check box, and then there are games where every decision hits hard and sticks with you. Shaping your journey from start to finish. These aren't just about good or bad endings. These are the games where your actions can lock you out of content.
